{"tid":2211132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾 2500 機密檔案：匯豐渣打摩通等跨國銀行　服務毒犯、黑幫、恐怖組織","createTime":"2020-09-21T02:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T04:07:08.000Z","uid":19527,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac7af0a64f931bbe23302887896a3a5856b9f98","tid":2211132,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"來自 88 個國家，超過 400 名記者參與的國際調查聯盟洗錢調查專案，耗時 16 個月，調查超過 2500 份被洩的美國政府機密文件，揭露包括摩根大通、匯豐控股等多家跨國銀行近 20 年來，涉嫌違反國際反洗黑錢共識，容許罪犯、被制裁的國家、機構轉移資金。當中包括讓俄羅斯權貴成功避開國際制裁，以及匯豐涉嫌容許屬投資騙局的 8000 萬美元資金轉移。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E9%80%BE-2500-%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88-%E5%8C%AF%E8%B1%90%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E6%91%A9%E9%80%9A%E7%AD%89%E8%B7%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%AF%92%E7%8A%AF-%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB-%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94/?fbclid=IwAR1v483SlKWsOsz0W39SHKCYWYKH130wUGscQ29X8IY-eNCn23uNihyqRi0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E9%2580%25BE-2500-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%258C%25AF%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2591%25A9%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B9%25AB-%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1v483SlKWsOsz0W39SHKCYWYKH130wUGscQ29X8IY-eNCn23uNihyqRi0&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=c3f9a7c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E9%2580%25BE-2500-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%258C%25AF%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2591%25A9%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B9